        "TileImage": "$($repository b8f0bf6c-4826-4de2-a785-2d139967e09c).Image",
        "Description": "Haven is done. And well done on it to. Now is the time to really start the plan. We are starting small. A neighbourhood called Whittleton Creek. We selected this neighbourhood for a good reason. Lately, alot of break in has accured and two owners tasked themself with ensuring the safety of the neighbourhood. Your task is to clearout the neighbourhood and kill three primary targets. Nolan Cassidy and Gunther Mueller have started a watch of sorts, real gun-nuts. And the local sheriff Daren Swart.",
